<h1>Become a Sponsor!</h1>

<p>SLC .NET is always looking for sponsors. Whether you're interested in providing a one-time sponsorship or donating on
  a recurring basis, we will gladly work with you.</p>

<p>We can accept monetary donations, goods and/or services provided strictly for the benefit of SLC .NET members. SLC
  .NET is a registered 501(c)(3) Nonprofit and can provide our ID number for tax purposes as needed.</p>

<h2>Start Sponsoring</h2>
<p>To get started sponsoring us please reach out via <a data-email-ug href="mailto:slc.netug@gmail.com">email</a>!</p>

<h2>Why you should partner with us</h2>
<p><em>Mission</em> - We aim to bring the .NET community together every month to 
advance our knowledge and share our passion for these technologies.</p>
<p>Join us and our community of over 1,500 software professionals.</p>

<h2>Perks</h2>
<p>Sponsor recognition at event(s) - including signage, program mention, appropriate
marketing materials, and swag bag opportunities where applicable.</p>
<p>Logo on website, meetup, and event information.</p>

<h2>SLC.NET Con Sponsorship Levels</h2>
<h3>Bronze - $100</h3>
<p>Company included on "Partner's Page" on our website for 6 months.</p>

<h3>Silver - $500</h3>
<p>Company name, logo, and sponsorship level included in all event programming
and promotional materials (including flyers, pamphlets, t-shirts, and merchandise).</p>
<p>Company included on "Partner's Page" on our website for 1 year.</p>

<h3>Gold - $1,000</h3>
<p>Company name, logo, and sponsorship level included in all event programming
and promotional materials (including flyers, pamphlets, t-shirts, and merchandise).</p>
<p>Company included on "Partner's Page" on our website for 2 years.</p>
<p>Live shout out / acknowledgement during the event.</p>

<h2>Monthly Sponsorship Opportunities</h2>
<p>We are consistently searching for partners to sponsor dinner and prizes for our monthly in-person meetings. Please
  note: in-person meetings have been suspended for the rest of 2020 due to COVID-19.</p>
<p>If you would rather contribute financially, we can accept donations of two tiers, as listed below, to spend on food,
  drinks, prizes, and other swag for meetings.</p>

<h3>Bronze - $100</h3>
<p>Company included in meeting materials with live shout out / acknowledgement during the event.</p>

<h3>Silver - $500</h3>
<p>Live shout out / acknowledgement during the event.</p>
<p>Company name, logo, and sponsorship level included on Meetup page for 1 year.</p>

<h3>Gold - $1,000</h3>
<p>Have something in mind? Please <a data-email-ug href="mailto:slc.netug@gmail.com">reach out</a>.</p>

